name: MigraineDiagnosisICD
title: Migraine diagnosis (ICD)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set includes ICD9CM and ICD10CM concepts for migraine headache.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify people diagnosed with migraine headache. This element may map to "Diagnosis" Category of the Quality Data Model.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts for migraine headache (pain in head).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts for cyclical vomiting, ophthalmoplegic migraine, and abdominal migraine.)
